NINJASK moves around at such a high
speed that it cannot be seen, even
while its crying can be clearly heard. For that reason, this POKMON was long
believed to be invisible.

If NINJASK is not trained properly,
it will refuse to obey the TRAINER and
cry loudly continuously. Because of this quality, this POKMON
is said to be one that puts the
TRAINERs abilities to the test.

Because it darts about vigorously at high
speed, it is very difficult to see. Hearing
its distinctive cries for too long induces
a headache.

This POKMON is so quick, it is said to
be able to avoid any attack. It loves to
feed on tree sap.
